## 🔐 SECURITY IMPLEMENTATION

### ✅ Authentication Layer
- [x] Login required untuk semua routes
- [x] Credentials validated dengan strict
- [x] Password harus match
- [x] Username case-sensitive
- [x] Error messages clear & informative

### ✅ Authorization Layer
- [x] Role-based access control (RBAC)
- [x] Only admin/super_admin dapat akses
- [x] Non-admin users automatically blocked
- [x] Automatic redirect ke login jika unauthorized
- [x] Session validation setiap page load

### ✅ Session Management
- [x] Session stored di localStorage
- [x] Survives page refresh
- [x] Survives browser close (sampai cleared)
- [x] Logout clears session completely
- [x] Multiple tabs synchronized

### ✅ Protected Routes
- [x] 14+ dashboard routes protected
- [x] All sub-routes protected
- [x] Login route accessible tanpa auth
- [x] Default redirect to login
- [x] Navbar/Sidebar only visible when authenticated

