## 📁 FILES MODIFIED (5 TOTAL)

### 1️⃣ `src/contexts/AuthContext.js` ✅
**Changes Made**:
```javascript
✅ Added super_admin role support
✅ Default users: admin + superadmin
✅ Login validates role (admin/super_admin only)
✅ RegisterUser only allows admin/super_admin
✅ Session stored in localStorage
✅ Error handling for unauthorized roles
```

**Key Methods**:
- `login(username, password)` - Validates credentials & role
- `logout()` - Clears session & localStorage
- `registerUser(username, password, role)` - Create new admin/super_admin

---

### 2️⃣ `src/components/ProtectedRoute.js` ✅
**Changes Made**:
```javascript
✅ Check if user authenticated
✅ Check if user role is admin/super_admin
✅ Redirect unauthorized to login
✅ Handle loading states gracefully
✅ Support role-based restrictions
```

**Logic**:
```
1. Check isAuthenticated
   NO → Redirect to /login
2. Check role (admin or super_admin?)
   NO → Redirect to /login
3. All checks passed → Render children
```

---

### 3️⃣ `src/App.js` ✅
**Changes Made**:
```javascript
✅ Wrap app with <AuthProvider>
✅ Wrap all routes with <ProtectedRoute>
✅ Added Login route (public)
✅ Protected all 14+ dashboard routes
✅ Default redirect to /login
✅ Split into App() and AppContent()
```

**Route Structure**:
```
/login                  → Public (No protection)
/dashboard              → Protected
/panel-distribusi       → Protected
/trafo                  → Protected
/laporan                → Protected
/dashboard/*            → Protected
/                       → Redirect to /login
/*                      → Redirect to /login
```

---

