## 🎯 USER JOURNEY

```
User opens: http://localhost:3001
         ↓
[AuthProvider checks localStorage]
         ↓
Is user authenticated?
    YES ↙ NO ↘
         ↓
    YES → Show Dashboard
              (Navbar + Sidebar)
    
    NO → Show Login Page
             (Demo buttons available)
             ↓
         User clicks demo button
             ↓
         Fields auto-filled
             ↓
         User clicks Login
             ↓
         [Validate credentials]
         [Check role]
         ↓
         Valid? YES → Save to localStorage
                      Navigate to /dashboard
         Valid? NO  → Show error message
                      Stay on login page
```

---

## 🔄 FLOW DIAGRAM

### Login Success Flow
```
Input Credentials
      ↓
AuthContext.login()
      ↓
Validate role (admin/super_admin?)
      ↓
YES → Save to localStorage
    → Save currentUser
    → setIsAuthenticated(true)
    → Return success
    → Navigate to /dashboard
```

### Protected Route Flow
```
User accesses /dashboard
      ↓
ProtectedRoute component
      ↓
Check isAuthenticated
      ↓
NO → Redirect to /login
YES → Check role
      ↓
NOT admin/super_admin → Redirect to /login
YES → Render component
```

